rows.label: tlk42300012_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Here is fact that not many
people know.

rows.label: tlk42300012_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Goldmund actually powered
by manual labor!

rows.label: tlk42300012_04_msg0003
rows.name:
There is secret room somewhere in
Goldmund with running wheel...

rows.label: tlk42300012_04_msg0004
rows.name:
And force of Nopon running in wheel
is what drive Goldmund Divine Beast to move!

rows.label: tlk42300012_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Goldmund Divine Beast very lazy beast,
so not move at all without significant
Noponforce pressure.

rows.label: tlk42300012_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Tondon only know about this
because was assigned to running
wheel repairs once.

rows.label: tlk42300012_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Friends best not go spreading
this around, okay?
